	   <tr><td>Title:</td><td id= colspan=1></td></tr>
	   <tr><td>Journal Rating:</td><td><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/star.gif><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/star.gif><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/star.gif><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/star.gif><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/star.gif></td></tr><tr><td>Email:<td><a href=Mailto:Salura@allakhazam.com>Salura@allakhazam.com</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2 id=headerrow>Bio:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2>Salura is the twin to Salur the cleric. Salura is the Matriarch of Clan Ater'Mors a collection of a total of 16 member;, 6 family, 10 hired mercenarries, bent on avenging the death of Salut and Rana, the parents of Salura and her siblings by a band of maurading Edudites.  You can read more about it and the Clan's progress in the journal.</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></center>
